{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01LLfe3bAjuvzU5J7BfQHFwJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cross-namespace connectivity is working (200 OK). The monitoring ES is reachable from the elasticsearch namespace.\n\nCurrent volumes in the StatefulSet: `es-config`, `es-plugins`, `es-keystore`, `es-secure-settings`.\n\nNow I'm ready to create all the resources. Let me write the YAML files and apply them.\n\nI'll create:\n1. ConfigMap `es-log4j2` - modified log4j2.properties with file-based appender for server logs\n2. ConfigMap `metricbeat-monitoring-config` - metricbeat.yml\n3. ConfigMap `filebeat-monitoring-config` - filebeat.yml\n4. Patch StatefulSet `es-cluster` to add volumes and sidecars\n\nElasticsearch sets the logs base path to `/usr/share/elasticsearch/logs` by default, so the server log file will end up at `/usr/share/elasticsearch/logs/es-cluster_server.json`. Now I'm writing out all the YAML manifests.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":10271,"cache_read_input_tokens":53881,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":10271},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"77ff193e-e364-4989-988e-248143808fa8","uuid":"892740b5-20b4-4942-a9d8-c0586f826ffd","request_id":"req_011CcfyadBuads9LWCbnfPvd"}
